{"tid":519582,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【動畫點評】Just Because!","createTime":"2018-01-04T13:33:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T13:59:52.000Z","uid":135630,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"aa70c1d684e683feff574f49d70d5ecf96f1af1b","tid":519582,"uid":135630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T13:33:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yqVq9iL7iBk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyqVq9iL7iBk&d=hA8a%2BddWznd2NUoDpJQQ00%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=127f9bfe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yqVq9iL7iBk</a><br />\n<br />\n小弟試做動畫點評，純粹興趣使然。<br />\n台灣大陸呢類點評都好多，自問都做得都唔好，<br />\n但仍然想嘗試下，以粵語分享個人嘅睇法。<br />\n希望咁多位大佬畀面睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講得唔好的話歡迎狠插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"118ef428c9442bed34118decf255a6e1c2e8ff88","tid":519582,"uid":35667,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T13:42:15.000Z","msg":"字幕字體...."},{"pid":"76cbb359e456a8492f8fc1e980b04c136fc647b2","tid":519582,"uid":14065,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T13:48:02.000Z","msg":"講劇情佔大部份<br />\n點評內容得好少<br />\n似谷阿莫多過評論"},{"pid":"4d411c5255fda18a906d8ed4bdbcce3aebbfc3d3","tid":519582,"uid":42425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T14:08:28.000Z","msg":"1 非劇透評論得一分鐘太短<br />\n2 唔洗禁斯文，壓住聲講野想訓"},{"pid":"5a610ae1f045a1b01a9b1e309d476de44cbfac1b","tid":519582,"uid":135630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"118ef428c9442bed34118decf255a6e1c2e8ff88","tid":519582,"uid":35667,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T13:42:15.000Z","msg":"字幕字體...."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T17:27:06.000Z","msg":"一直都用default，真係好礙眼咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{